<plot>At major events like agricultural fairs, there are always those sales reps called pitchmen. Armed with novelty gadgets and (hopefully) a silver tongue, they ply their trade to the public in the hopes of making that all important sale. This film follows one major sales rep in this line of work as he manages his growing business and dreams of where his line of work will take him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434124</url></doc>
